[normal]The Chairman:[bold] The problem we have is that we know there are people who are hanging out there, who have left school at the age of 16 and they do not appear in this because they are not paid until 18. So what happens? You are assuming they are all in education, is that it?
[normal]Alex Conway[bold]: No.
[normal]The Chairman:[bold] Oh, no, sorry, you do not because you go for 16 to 24 year-olds.
