[normal]Lord Fearn:[bold] Three times now you have mentioned schools, and you mentioned leaflets going into schools in the last report. What happens about the feedback? Who gets the feedback? Who is responsible for getting the feedback to you? Or are you happy with no feedback at all? Do you wait for the individuals to reply?
